caption: This week we are going to explore the Rancocas Creek that flows through Burlington County. From our photo collection we have some images of a flood of Mason’s Creek around 1940. Mason’s Creek is a tributary of the Rancocas. The flood was so severe that it damaged the bridge near Creek Road and Marne Highway. #Rancocas #Creeks #Floods #BurlingtonCounty
Heavy rain lashes #SriLanka triggering #floods and #landslides that have killed at least 17 people and forced tens of thousands from their homes
